{"tid":1789006,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日本美女記者指控26歲時遭男記者強姦    獲東京法院裁定民事勝訴","createTime":"2019-12-19T06:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-19T09:01:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"f148a6af1b42398f534ba0a4113803b5d44b710c","tid":1789006,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/s4aEyTgzBJnDX8wAh5kmJg--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-12/caeb1f30-21e7-11ea-ad9d-3a0d911eb560\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fs4aEyTgzBJnDX8wAh5kmJg--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-12%2Fcaeb1f30-21e7-11ea-ad9d-3a0d911eb560&h=259e6173&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本女記者伊藤詩織指控被男記者山口敬之強姦的案件，獲日本東京法院裁定民事勝訴，涉事男記者須賠償330萬日圓。伊藤得悉裁決後，在法院門外舉起印有「勝訴」的字牌。山口則否認指控，將會提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15326098045784fe641e1bc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2Fpgc-image%2F15326098045784fe641e1bc&h=f6b0e5f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伊藤詩織表示，在2015年4月，希望獲時任TBS新聞台華盛頓分台台長、被稱為安倍晉三「御用記者」的山口介紹工作機會，與他去到東京一間餐廳共晉晚餐，但飲酒之後失去意識，醒來時發現被帶到酒店，躺在床上，懷疑是被下藥迷姦。<br />\n<br />\n伊藤事後報警，但案件聲稱因證據不足而被中止處理。伊藤之後在2017年出書談及事件，並向山口民事索償1100萬日圓，但山口反告伊藤侵犯名譽，索賠1億3000萬日圓。法院裁定山口敗訴。"},{"pid":"eb90d3942e1fce19399aa6ab2bb5372fa29b1258","tid":1789006,"uid":165749,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"好令"},{"pid":"79e8676b6279433c042957d15aadba57e6bb74d1","tid":1789006,"uid":36995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"靚女記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66784dae140c7171a0dd81f3c15732909d914772","tid":1789006,"uid":137569,"like":10,"di